1989;;Blaze;;American;;Ron Shelton;;Paul Newman, Lolita Davidovich;;drama, biography;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blaze_(1989_film);;The movie tells the highly fictionalized story of the latter years of Earl Long, a flamboyant Governor of Louisiana, brother of assassinated governor and U.S. Senator Huey P. Long and uncle of longtime U.S. Senator Russell Long. According to the novel and film, Earl Long allegedly fell in love with a young stripper named Blaze Starr.